'''NetherRealm Studios'''（藝術化字體為 '''NetheЯRealm Studios'''）是總部設於美國[[芝加哥|芝加哥]]和[[伊利諾州|伊利諾州]]的[[電子遊戲開發商|遊戲開發者]]。NetherRealm Studios 於2010年5月成立以取代[[華納兄弟互動娛樂|華納兄弟互動娛樂]]的華納遊戲芝加哥分公司。NetherRealm Studios由共同創作過《[[真人快打|真人快打]]》的資深[[遊戲程序師|遊戲程序師]]{{link-en|艾德·布恩|Ed Boom|艾德·布恩}}負責，開發的[[格鬥遊戲|格鬥遊戲]]有《真人快打系列》和《超級英雄：武力對決系列》。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://kotaku.com/5620295/whats-next-for-mortal-kombat-netherrealm-studios |title=What's Next For Mortal Kombat, NetherRealm Studios |first=Michael |last=McWhertor |date=2010-08-24 |website=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]] |accessdate=2020-08-06 |archive-date=2018-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181115095950/https://kotaku.com/5620295/whats-next-for-mortal-kombat-netherrealm-studios |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==歷史==
2009年2月12日，持有《[[真人快打|真人快打]]》[[智慧財產權|智慧財產權]]的遊戲開發商[[Midway_Games|Midway Games]]依據[[美國破產法第十一章|美國破產法第十一章]]在美國提出破產申請。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/midway-us-files-for-chapter-11 |title=Midway US files for reorganisation in Bankruptcy Court |first=James |last=Lee |date=2009-02-12 |website=[[GamesIndustry.biz|GamesIndustry.biz]] |accessdate=2020-08-07 |archive-date=2018-09-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180912054650/https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/midway-us-files-for-chapter-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://kotaku.com/5152300/midway-files-for-bankruptcy |title=Midway Files for Bankruptcy |first=Brian |last=Crecente |date=2009-02-12 |website=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]] |accessdate=2020-08-07 |archive-date=2017-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171222104823/https://kotaku.com/5152300/midway-files-for-bankruptcy |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[華納兄弟|華納兄弟]]之後在2009年7月10日獲得了Midway Games包括《真人快打》、《{{link-en|這是維加斯|This Is Vegas|這是維加斯}}》和公司[[組織結構|組織結構]]的大多數資產。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://kotaku.com/5312018/warner-bros-now-owns-midway-mortal-kombat |title=Warner Bros. Now Owns Midway, Mortal Kombat |first=Michael |last=McWhertor |date=2009-07-10 |website=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]] |accessdate=2020-08-07 |archive-date=2013-05-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130513024227/https://kotaku.com/5312018/warner-bros-now-owns-midway-mortal-kombat |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.gamespot.com/articles/midway-newcastle-shuttered-chicago-layoffs-imminent/1100-6213354/ |title=Midway Newcastle shuttered, Chicago layoffs 'imminent' |first=Tor |last=Thorsen |date=2009-07-14 |website=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |accessdate=2020-08-07 |archive-date=2017-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171222051311/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/midway-newcastle-shuttered-chicago-layoffs-imminent/1100-6213354/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>當華納兄弟關閉多數 Midway Games 設於[[芝加哥|伊利諾州芝加哥]]、[[聖地牙哥_(加利福尼亞州)|加州聖地牙哥]]和[[利物浦|英格蘭利物浦]]的總部和開發工作室時，只保留了 Midway Games 芝加哥開發工作室，並將其納入[[華納兄弟互動娛樂|華納兄弟互動娛樂]]旗下。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.gamespot.com/articles/midways-chicago-hq-closing-final-buyout-price-49-million/1100-6213488/ |title=Midway's Chicago HQ closing, final buyout price $49 million |first=Tor |last=Thorsen |date=2009-07-16 |website=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |accessdate=2020-08-07 |archive-date=2018-08-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180828055829/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/midways-chicago-hq-closing-final-buyout-price-49-million/1100-6213488/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.engadget.com/2009/07/17/midway-execs-get-the-boot-entire-chicago-dev-team-acquired-by-w/ |title=Midway execs get the boot, entire Chicago dev team acquired by WB |first=Ben |last=Gilbert |date=2009-07-17 |website=[[Engadget|Engadget]] |accessdate=2020-08-07 |archive-date=2015-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151016135325/https://www.engadget.com/2009/07/17/midway-execs-get-the-boot-entire-chicago-dev-team-acquired-by-w/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>該工作室幾天後更名為華納遊戲芝加哥分公司。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.engadget.com/2009/07/27/mortal-kombat-team-sheds-midway-skin-for-wb-games-chicago/ |title=Mortal Kombat team sheds Midway skin for 'WB Games Chicago' |first=Ben |last=Gilbert |date=2009-07-27 |website=[[Engadget|Engadget]] |accessdate=2020-08-07 |archive-date=2016-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160112090215/https://www.engadget.com/2009/07/27/mortal-kombat-team-sheds-midway-skin-for-wb-games-chicago/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/mortal-kombat-studio-becomes-wb-games-chicago |title=Mortal Kombat studio becomes WB Games Chicago |first=Matt |last=Martin |date=2009-07-28 |website=[[GamesIndustry.biz|GamesIndustry.biz]] |accessdate=2020-08-07 |archive-date=2012-08-02 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20120802064119/http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/mortal-kombat-studio-becomes-wb-games-chicago |dead-url=no }}</ref>2010年4月20日，工作室改組為 NetherRealm Studios，取代了華納遊戲芝加哥分公司。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.vg247.com/2010/04/09/warner-trademarks-netherrealm-studios/ |title=Warner trademarks Netherrealm Studios |first=Stephany |last=Nunneley |date=2010-04-09 |website=[[VG247|VG247]] |accessdate=2020-08-07 |archive-date=2018-08-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180828170351/https://www.vg247.com/2010/04/09/warner-trademarks-netherrealm-studios/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.shacknews.com/article/64202/mortal-kombat-returning-to-2d |title=Mortal Kombat Returning to '2D' Roots |first=Alice |last=O'Connor |date=2010-06-10 |website=[[Shacknews|Shacknews]] |accessdate=2020-08-07 |archive-date=2018-09-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180912091907/https://www.shacknews.com/article/64202/mortal-kombat-returning-to-2d |dead-url=no }}</ref>

NetherRealm Studios 的第一款遊戲是《{{link-en|真人快打 (2011年遊戲)|Mortal Kombat (2011 video game)|真人快打}}》，這款發行於2011年4月的遊戲是真人快打系列的第九作也是《真人快打系列》的重啟作品。他們以[[DC宇宙|DC宇宙]]為題材的遊戲《[[超級英雄：武力對決|超級英雄：武力對決]]》在2013年發售。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.engadget.com/2013/01/15/injustice-gods-among-us-hits-april-16-batte-edition-revealed/ |title=Injustice: Gods Among Us hits April 16, Battle Edition revealed |first=Sinan |last=Kubba |date=2013-01-15|website=[[Engadget|Engadget]] |accessdate=2020-08-07 |archive-date=2016-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160413102437/https://www.engadget.com/2013/01/15/injustice-gods-among-us-hits-april-16-batte-edition-revealed/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2013-01-15-injustice-gods-among-us-release-date-19th-april |title=Injustice: Gods Among Us release date 19th April |first=Robert |last=Purchese |date=2013-01-15 |website=eurogamer.net |accessdate=2020-08-07 |archive-date=2020-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809012739/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2013-01-15-injustice-gods-among-us-release-date-19th-april |dead-url=no }}</ref>這兩款遊戲的成功促使了相關續作的誕生，分別是2015年發行的《[[真人快打X|真人快打X]]》和2017年的《[[超級英雄：武力對決2|超級英雄：武力對決2]]》<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.gamespot.com/articles/injustice-2-release-date-revealed-update/1100-6446713/ |title=Injustice 2 Release Date Revealed [UPDATE] |first=Kallie |last=Plagge |date=2017-01-09 |website=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |accessdate=2020-08-07 |archive-date=2017-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170110102844/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/injustice-2-release-date-revealed-update/1100-6446713/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://kotaku.com/injustice-2-doubles-up-on-cats-1792349606 |title=Injustice 2 Doubles Up On Cats |first=Mike |last=Fahey |date=2017-02-14 |website=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]] |accessdate=2020-08-07 |archive-date=2017-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171222051834/https://kotaku.com/injustice-2-doubles-up-on-cats-1792349606 |dead-url=no }}</ref>同時，NetherRealm Studios 也研發了《{{link-en|蝙蝠俠：阿卡漢城市 封閉|Batman: Arkham City Lockdown|蝙蝠俠：阿卡漢城市 封閉}}》、《{{link-en|蝙蝠俠：阿卡漢起源 (手機版)|Batman: Arkham Origins (mobile)|蝙蝠俠：阿卡漢起源}}》和《{{link-en|WWE 不朽傳奇|WWE Immortals|WWE 不朽傳奇}}》的[[Android|Android]]和[[iOS|iOS]]版本。 NetherRealm Studios 的最新遊戲《[[真人快打11|真人快打11]]》於2019年4月23日發售。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://kotaku.com/mortal-kombat-11-announced-launching-globally-april-23-1830923742 |title=''Mortal Kombat 11'' Announced, Launching Globally April 23 |first=Mike |last=Fahey |date=2018-12-06 |website=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]] |accessdate=2020-08-07 |archive-date=2018-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181207091742/https://kotaku.com/mortal-kombat-11-announced-launching-globally-april-23-1830923742 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

